abstract: Pete Buttigieg, the only veteran in the top tier of candidates seeking the Democratic presidential nomination, is turning to South Carolina's large military community to help shore up his nagging lack of support among black voters.
snippet: Pete Buttigieg, the only veteran in the top tier of candidates seeking the Democratic presidential nomination, is turning to South Carolina's large military community to help shore up his nagging lack of support among black voters.
lead_paragraph: CHARLESTON, S.C. — Pete Buttigieg, the only veteran in the top tier of candidates seeking the Democratic presidential nomination, is turning to South Carolina's large military community to help shore up his nagging lack of support among black voters.
headline_main: Buttigieg Courts South Carolina Black Voters With His Veteran Status
headline_print_headline: Buttigieg Courts South Carolina Black Voters With His Veteran Status

abstract: The president’s visit with Prime Minister Narendra Modi included a rally in a cricket stadium, stops at historic Indian sites and trade talks.
snippet: The president’s visit with Prime Minister Narendra Modi included a rally in a cricket stadium, stops at historic Indian sites and trade talks.
lead_paragraph: On the second day of President Trump’s trip to India, he and Prime Minister Narendra Modi appeared before reporters in the lush garden of Hyderabad House, the iconic building typically used to host foreign leaders.

abstract: President Trump’s border wall is beginning to rise, but a thick curtain of policy changes is more responsible for suppressing the flow of immigrants into the country.
snippet: President Trump’s border wall is beginning to rise, but a thick curtain of policy changes is more responsible for suppressing the flow of immigrants into the country.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Trump’s immigration policies — from travel bans and visa restrictions to refugee caps and asylum changes — have begun to deliver on a longstanding goal: Legal immigration has fallen more than 11 percent and a steeper drop is looming.

abstract: It would have derailed the lives of many of the ancestors we celebrate.
snippet: It would have derailed the lives of many of the ancestors we celebrate.
lead_paragraph: Americans love stories about immigrants — especially when they are about our parents, grandparents, and great-grandparents. We admire these people’s courage and grit. We acknowledge their sacrifices and the vital roles they played in getting us where we are and building this country. My own grandfather, an immigrant from Mexico, worked as a taxi driver and a gravedigger, among other occupations, to support his family. Today we count professors and lawyers among his progeny.

abstract: Fears of a potential party wipeout may be overstated. But it’s not hard to understand their theoretical basis.
snippet: Fears of a potential party wipeout may be overstated. But it’s not hard to understand their theoretical basis.
lead_paragraph: Swing-district House Democrats don’t agree on which candidate they want to lead them on the ticket this year, but they do seem to agree on which candidate they don’t: Bernie Sanders.
